{"tid":1492573,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"咁大單警犬虐老案 堆NGO潛哂水？","createTime":"2019-08-21T01:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T13:39:12.000Z","uid":265048,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0455475ea873989000c91c3f5d07b13f80698b1b","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a12d30905df6f86a0f96fefe9847c4948b58d20","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推十連"},{"pid":"f172e81650611943cfb1bd13f350449daabdea22","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推十連<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/housing/socialservices/elderly/elderlyservices.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fhousing%2Fsocialservices%2Felderly%2Felderlyservices.htm&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41Dk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=b7282934\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/housing/socialservices/elderly/elderlyservices.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6867d755e991092341d5e5bf2cd109adc75d58aa","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:46:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkcss.org.hk/c/cont_detail.asp?type_id=2&amp;content_id=5298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcss.org.hk%2Fc%2Fcont_detail.asp%3Ftype_id%3D2%26content_id%3D5298&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41Dk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=94ad1ca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkcss.org.hk/c/cont_detail.asp?type_id=2&amp;content_id=5298</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>出動幾十警員圍捕手無寸鐵的少女、粗言辱罵巿民/記者/社工/救護人員、持續向已被制伏的示威者施暴、近距離鳴槍和追打正在撤離的群眾，這些都在鏡頭面前發生。如果這就是所謂的相應和適當武力，又如何說服得了公眾。相對於7.21當天警方面對白衣暴徒的無所作為，實在有太大的差異。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所最新一份民調顯示，巿民對警隊的滿意度由六月初反修例運動爆發前的61分急跌至39.4分，是2012年有紀錄以來最低，同時有58%巿民認為警察在最近警民衝突中使用的武力過大。<br />\n<br />\n然而，到目前為止，沒有涉嫌違規的警員受查或被處分，而且根本無法鑑別警員身份，投訴無門，公眾今後又如何信服警隊會持守誓詞：遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律，以不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠、努力的態度行使職權，執行職務。<br />\n<br />\n警隊公信力幾近盡毀，政府若不能對警隊建立有效的制約及平衡(check and balance)機制，將難以重建市民對警隊的信心。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5ebb1c07b39450f8fbe72d1cdc017135cf5fcacb","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b50c4ab66cfc1645f0c64129b1be527b36296af","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a887388ff6df43e59b2e71e22bb7c0e2b14779c4","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次會唔會禁平安鐘就有狗黎打鑊金"},{"pid":"25d93e0a85a2a8abd73d6e48ec534daa35278eb2","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe01c4ab930bb2435e9f5f0a958d44947af08802","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有銀髮族幫緊我地唔可以忘記"},{"pid":"f318cdc01c2c3e8a2a41ec732ab463c8e0b47d8b","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSilver Hair We Connect"},{"pid":"698ed47ce52663b3830c99e22acaaed3a709c69a","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f581e376dad035e9987f95e2884a59ece0a16aa","tid":1492573,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:01:18.000Z","msg":"【塞爆社署，表述民情，嚴正討論】<br />\n<br />\n行動形式：向深水埗地區社署福利專員，作出嚴正質詢和討論。<br />\n<br />\n行動日期及時間：<br />\n8月23日(五）10am-1pm<br />\n<br />\n行動地點：深水埗南昌邨南昌社區中心高座3樓<br />\n<br />\n嚴正討論內容：<br />\n1.深水埗街坊受催淚影響<br />\n2.警察虐老（向長者濫用私刑）<br />\n3.老人院中催淚彈<br />\n4.社工在場作人道支援被捕<br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n1. 此項活動與區內前線工作及服務息息相關，請該區服務的同工以工時出動。<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">若深水埗DO回應未令人滿意，下次行動唯有直接到胡忠。</span></span><br />\n3. 黃帽/黑衫為記<br />\n<br />\n#轉載<br />\n#反送中社福聯合陣線<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oW5RgA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oW5RgA.jpg&h=95b8cd87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d21d2c1e5ebf8559300cc139e051e773a86f192","tid":1492573,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6z7q5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6z7q5Y.jpg&h=cc2f3dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MpTzQxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpTzQxD.jpg&h=8a83645e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SD7g3SE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSD7g3SE.jpg&h=c3d87592&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMxkL50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMxkL50.jpg&h=712e21f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGNMGEk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGNMGEk.jpg&h=be0e5720&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zDmBjq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzDmBjq1.jpg&h=4071fb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvdj1Em.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnvdj1Em.jpg&h=c91c4ec7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51bd6b884e75148f7899e0c0b5b28d894efe6602","tid":1492573,"uid":76370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:54:29.000Z","msg":"食屎狗"},{"pid":"210f9c5a00f9a7bba2a79911b64bbd2b9b1b2014","tid":1492573,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8a397a17b0c6b6589cdb21c1f420672af004cb","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210f9c5a00f9a7bba2a79911b64bbd2b9b1b2014","tid":1492573,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"NGO 咬政府錢，即你納稅人既錢<br />\n社企未必咬政府，但亦都有唔少方法令到市民同機構捐錢<br />\n<br />\n只不過虐老個大個議題竟然冇一間出聲"},{"pid":"d4ff57f8fe81755e673a8646aa03a0f7f3bcfb66","tid":1492573,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b8a397a17b0c6b6589cdb21c1f420672af004cb","tid":1492573,"uid":265048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210f9c5a00f9a7bba2a79911b64bbd2b9